!!! IMPORTANT !!!

This tool will dump your whole database into a file that can be downloaded viw ftp
and maybe via http depending on your site configuration. Do not use this script 
if you database contains sensitive information such as passwords, users datasâ€¦

How to use :

1- Add your database connexion information in dumpdb.php
2- Upload dumpdb.php to your remote shared server
3- Add ftp connection information in backup.sh
4- you can backup by executing ./backup.sh